AmaZulu Traditional Prime Minister, Prince Mangosuthu Buthelezi is about to provide an update on royal matters. Prince MisuZulu ascended to the throne last week as the heir apparent to his late father, King Goodwill Zwelithini. It follows the passing of his mother, Queen Shiyiwe Mantfombi Dlamini Zulu.   * Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. DURBAN - AmaZulu Traditional Prime Minister Prince Mangosuthu Buthelezi is giving an update on royal matters. Prince MisuZulu ascended to the throne last week as the heir apparent to his late father, King Goodwill Zwelithini. It follows the passing of his mother, Queen Shiyiwe Mantfombi Dlamini Zulu.